{
  "stem": "26790.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I told myself, if I will be able to find a place where can sit down, I would have a rest for few minutes, a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As the moon was coming out, I saw maybe a few meters from me, a tree was cutted off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The tree was cut off not to the ground, cut off a little bit higher to be able to sit there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as you know, what strict regulations is in the army, you [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You're not allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You're not allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I sit down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mention, ?] I fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What I done?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how long I was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think that that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], my, the man from, from, from the regiment, when the rain stopped, the moon was coming out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He decided to go have a look around if everything is in order, the guard is in order, everything is in order.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As he saw, the moon was shining to the bayonet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the bayonet doesn't move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's mean somebody is sleeping or something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he started come to me, started come to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as he was already a few meters from me, suddenly, I wake up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what's hap-- I wake up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I open my eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I saw [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He stretch his arm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He want grab my rifle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If he would grab my rifle, he would took the rifle to headquarters, I get shot sleeping on the-- sleeping on guard.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I wake up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know what's happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I move away from this tree.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I move away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he comes to me closer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He called me, Ganc.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
